::Ramulus/Slayer/Firearm/Proto/Smokescreen::

Slayer growls as he hears Prebon's voice over his comm. He was just getting 
warmed up with these Maximals....

"I will be back, Maximal," he says to Ramulus, a missile firing off at 
Ramulus as Slayer activates his jetpack, flying up and trying to shake 
SnowCat off his leaking leg. The rocket hits Ramulus straight on, sending the 
Maximal flying through several trees and landing in Stasis lock.

Slayer launches off again, ignoring Lunarpine's words as he speeds after 
Prebon. "Master," he says into his comm, "Ramulus is down. I am not sure if 
he's dead, I didn't have enough time to scan."
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Firearm lands near Lunarpine, Proto dropping down near him.

"They retreated?" Firearm asks just as Proto asks if they got the hostages 
back.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Smokescreen grunts, shifting Spears' weight as he walked. She was getting 
heavier every step (to him at least), and he didn't really like the smoke 
coming out of her head. He hoped they wouldn't have to replace her systems.

He walks on, complaining to himself.
